# applications.automation.analog-system-test.torch-extinguisher

Torch One-to-many Conversion Tool

This Git Repo only contains the python code necessary to compile torch modules. Please note that all pertinent module collateral exists in separate git repos.

Please refer to the PowerPoint and [Github Wiki](https://github.com/intel-restricted/applications.automation.analog-system-test.torch-extinguisher/wiki/Torch-Extinguisher) page for full usage of this tool!
